snippet: The University of Denver men's lacrosse team upset Duke last weekend and now will compete for an N.C.A.A. bid in the E.C.A.C. tournament.
abstract: The University of Denver men's lacrosse team upset Duke last weekend and now will compete for an N.C.A.A. bid in the E.C.A.C. tournament.

headline.main: After Defeating Duke, Denver Heads to E.C.A.C. Tournament
